rows.label: qst200216_msg0001
rows.name:
Alright, everything's gathered!
Well then, I'm setting off soon.

rows.label: qst200216_msg0002
rows.name:
Because the client is
eagerly waiting, you see.

rows.label: qst200216_msg0003
rows.name:
So, where are you
transporting this cargo to?

rows.label: qst200216_msg0005
rows.name: Do you know anything about the client?

rows.label: qst200216_msg0006
rows.name:
Ships like this carry and transport
cargo from various clients.

rows.label: qst200216_msg0007
rows.name:
So, I don't really know what I'm
carrying or who the client is.

rows.label: qst200216_msg0009
rows.name: Where will you hand over this cargo?

rows.label: qst200216_msg0010
rows.name:
My job ends when I unload
it at the port. What's
wrong? Is there something?

rows.label: qst200216_msg0012
rows.name:
Well then, I'm setting off. Thank
you, you really helped me out!
